      <title>蘇丹難民在襲擊後逃離衣索比亞的聯合國難民營</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/sudanese-refugees-flee-un-camp-ethiopia-following-attacks-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三名難民和聯合國表示，在一系列槍擊和搶劫事件後，至少有 1,000 名蘇丹難民逃離了聯合國在衣索比亞北部管理的難民營。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/sudanese-refugees-flee-un-camp-ethiopia-following-attacks-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:52:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
