      <title>巴西拒絕淡水河谷和必和必拓對馬裡亞納災難的和解提議</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazil-rejects-vale-bhp-settlement-offer-mariana-disaster-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西聯邦政府週五表示，巴西和聖埃斯皮里圖州拒絕了礦商淡水河谷和必和必拓提出的關於對 2015 年致命的馬裡亞納尾礦壩決堤事故進行賠償的提議。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazil-rejects-vale-bhp-settlement-offer-mariana-disaster-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:41:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
